OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782481686
OL,3,CMayor 'appalled' by video showing
OL,4,Cpolice clashing with girls
OL,6,FA video which appears to show South
OL,7,FYorkshire Police officers involved in
OL,8,Fa physical confrontation with a group
OL,9,Fof teenage girls has been described as
OL,10,F"nothing short of shocking" by the
OL,11,Fforce and "appalling" by the region's
OL,12,Fmayor.
OL,14,FIn the footage, shared widely on
OL,15,Fsocial media, officers appear to shove
OL,16,Fand strike girls wearing party dresses
OL,17,Fon a street in Rotherham.
OL,19,FOne officers draws a baton and two
OL,20,Fothers brandish Tasers as they are
OL,21,Fconfronted by a group of young people.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@[O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782481686
OL,3,CMayor 'appalled' by video showing
OL,4,Cpolice clashing with girls
OL,6,FIn a strongly worded statement, South
OL,7,FYorkshire Police said: "The short clip
OL,8,Fon social media of the police response
OL,9,Fto an incident in Rotherham over the
OL,10,Fweekend appears nothing short of
OL,11,Fshocking.
OL,13,F"Our PSD (professional standards
OL,14,Fdepartment) are reviewing this and all
OL,15,Favailable footage, including body-worn
OL,16,Fvideo, of the full response to the 999
OL,17,Fcall to understand what happened
OL,18,Fbefore, during, and after what is
OL,19,Fpublicly available."
OL,26,@oD@XOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782481686
OL,3,CMayor 'appalled' by video showing
OL,4,Cpolice clashing with girls
OL,6,FIt added that officers' actions were
OL,7,Fexpected to be "lawful, proportionate
OL,8,Fand fair".
OL,10,FMayor of South Yorkshire Oliver
OL,11,FCoppard said he was "appalled" by the
OL,12,Ffootage.
OL,14,F"I've asked the police, the chief
OL,15,Fconstable, as a matter of urgency, to
OL,16,Freview the evidence, and then if the
OL,17,Fhighest standards of police conduct
OL,18,Fhave not been met, then to take swift
OL,19,Faction.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782481686
OL,3,CMayor 'appalled' by video showing
OL,4,Cpolice clashing with girls
OL,6,F"I would expect the chief constable to
OL,7,Ftake the strongest possible action
OL,8,Fagainst the officers if they are
OL,9,Findeed found to have done wrongdoing.
OL,10,FThey have to look at the whole
OL,11,Fevidence - I don't want to prejudge
OL,12,Fwhat the whole evidence might show -
OL,13,Fand sometimes clips on social media
OL,14,Fcan be misleading.
OL,16,F"But on the face of what I've seen, I
OL,17,Fwas appalled by it."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782481686
OL,3,CMayor 'appalled' by video showing
OL,4,Cpolice clashing with girls
OL,6,FHowever, South Yorkshire Police
OL,7,FFederation, which represents rank and
OL,8,Ffile officers, said it had raised
OL,9,Fconcerns with the force about its
OL,10,Fstatement.
OL,12,FThe federation said in a statement:
OL,13,F"It goes without saying that short
OL,14,Fvideo clips of incidents rarely show a
OL,15,Ffull story.
OL,17,F"Police officers are accountable for
OL,18,Ftheir actions but must be allowed fair
OL,19,Fand due process as part of any
OL,20,Finvestigation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782481686
OL,3,CMayor 'appalled' by video showing
OL,4,Cpolice clashing with girls
OL,6,F"The federation are supporting the
OL,7,Fofficers involved and will be making
OL,8,Fno further comment while the incident
OL,9,Fis still under review."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/6
